<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Add module support for Zend_Translate similar to this solution:
<a href="http://blog.vandenbos.org/2009/07/09/zend-framework-per-module-translation-sources/">http://blog.vandenbos.org/2009/07/…</a></p>

<p>Every module has its own language dir, e.g.: application/modules/user/lang
The translations have to be ADDED to (not replace) the Zend_Translate-Instance and stored in Registry with the default 'Zend_Translate'-key</p>

